In the Land of Morning Calm / Im Lande der Morgenstille


Country: Germany, Korea
Genre: Documentary
Year: 1925
Duration: 1:57:34
Director: Norbert Weber 
Starring: Korean Benedictine missionaries
Description:
 The film was made by a Benedictine missionary, Father Norbert Weber, during his visit to Korea in 1925. This film was made to educate German audiences on the life and culture of Korea.
